<ns3019:section xmlns:ns3019="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.technologies.java.j2se.security.jaas.jaasAuthentication">
    
    <ns3020:title xmlns:ns3020="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">JAAS Authentication</ns3020:title>

<ns3021:para xmlns:ns3021="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">Authentication revolves around establishing and verifying a user's
identity. The approach may range from username/password authentication
to voice recognition, retina scanning and other technologies.</ns3021:para>

<ns3022:para xmlns:ns3022="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">The JAAS provides a standard interface for authentication, enabling one
to plug in any authentication technology. Thus, new technologies may be 
added without modifying the Java code using the authentication.</ns3022:para>
    
